'''Izem amaziɣ''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: ''Panthera leo leo'') d yiwet n [[tadfert|tedfert]] n [[izem|yizmawen]] [[angar|inegren]] deg uzɣar (lexla) deg iseggasen imezwura n [[tasut tis 20]], Izem amaziɣ yella yettidir deg [[Tafriqt n Ugafa|Tefrikt n ugafa]] llan wid id yeqqaren d akken izem amaziɣ yenger yakk deg useggas n 1940 maca kra n yizmawen llan zeddiɣ (mazal) ttidiren deg kra n [[talmat n iɣersiwen|telmatin n iɣersiwen]] d [[Asirk|isirken]] 

